Starbies served several oleato drinks iced, which gave no possible time or process for a mixing. This led to the drinks being ugly with the two liquids separating. Which also makes them gross because your first sip will always be oil. Also, scientifically it was a nightmare. Coffee is a food that… quickens our systems. And olive oil… does the same.
